Class GENTask<TSelf, TPrompt, TOutput>

Namespace
Glitch9.AIDevKit

Abstract base class for all generative AI tasks (text, image, audio). Supports text, image, and audio prompts with fluent configuration methods.

public abstract class GENTask<TSelf, TPrompt, TOutput> : IGENTask where TSelf : GENTask<TSelf, TPrompt, TOutput>
